@Node Main "InterBase Amiga Database"

Welcome to the InterBase help. This is not intended to replace the manual
but suplement it by giving a discription of most of Interwords functions.
For a more acurate and verboise description of InterBase's functions it is 
recomended that you consult your manual.



		Table of contents

 
